@startuml services_package
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 11
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package gui.services {
  ' ===== Clustering Service =====
  class ClusteringService {
    - {static} logger: Logger
    --
    + runClustering(data: Data, radius: double): ClusterSet
    + saveClustering(fileName: String, result: ClusteringResult): void
    + loadClustering(fileName: String): ClusteringResult
    - validateInputs(data: Data, radius: double): void
  }

  ' ===== Data Import Service =====
  class DataImportService {
    - {static} logger: Logger
    --
    + loadFromCSV(filePath: String): Data
    + loadFromDatabase(tableName: String): Data
    + loadFromSerializedFile(filePath: String): Data
    + loadIrisData(): Data
    - parseCSV(filePath: String): Data
    - connectToDatabase(): DbAccess
  }

  enum DataSource << NEW >> {
    HARDCODED
    IRIS
    CSV
    DATABASE
  }

  ' ===== Export Service =====
  class ExportService {
    - {static} logger: Logger
    --
    + exportToCsv(filePath: String, result: ClusteringResult): void
    + exportToTextReport(filePath: String, result: ClusteringResult): void
    + exportToZip(zipFilePath: String, result: ClusteringResult): void
    - escapeCSV(value: String): String
    - generateReadme(result: ClusteringResult): String
  }

  ' ===== Relazioni con qtServer =====
  ClusteringService ..> "mining.QTMiner" : <<uses>>
  ClusteringService ..> "mining.ClusterSet" : <<uses>>
  ClusteringService ..> "data.Data" : <<uses>>

  DataImportService ..> "data.Data" : <<creates>>
  DataImportService ..> "database.DbAccess" : <<uses>>
  DataImportService ..> "gui.utils.DatasetLoader" : <<uses>>

  ExportService ..> "gui.models.ClusteringResult" : <<uses>>
}

note right of ClusteringService
  Wrapper per QTMiner.

  Funzionalità:
  - Esecuzione clustering
  - Salvataggio risultati (.dmp)
  - Caricamento risultati
  - Logging operazioni
  - Gestione eccezioni

  Delega computazione a qtServer
end note

note top of DataImportService
  Import dati da sorgenti multiple.

  Sorgenti supportate:
  - Dataset Standard: Iris (150 tuple, 4 continui) **(NEW)**
  - CSV file (parsing con inferenza tipi)
  - Database MySQL (via JDBC)
  - File serializzati (.dmp)

  Enum DataSource (NEW v1.1):
  - HARDCODED: PlayTennis (14 tuple)
  - IRIS: Dataset standard UCI
  - CSV: File CSV generico
  - DATABASE: Tabella MySQL

  Dataset Iris caricato da resources tramite
  DatasetLoader utility.
end note

note bottom of ExportService
  Export risultati multipli formati.

  Formati:
  - CSV: Tabulare (ClusterID, TupleID, Distance, Attrs)
  - TXT: Report testuale con statistiche
  - ZIP: Pacchetto completo (.dmp + CSV + TXT + README)

  Timestamp automatico nei nomi file
end note

note as N1
  Pattern: Service Layer

  Controller → Service → qtServer

  Vantaggi:
  - Controller snelli (solo UI logic)
  - Business logic centralizzata
  - Riusabilità Services
  - Testing semplificato
end note

@enduml
